Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: adi.simplestructure
Version: 0.3
Summary: Removes top and footer viewlets and adds portlets instead.
Home-page: http://svn.plone.org/svn/collective/
Author: Ida Ebkes
Author-email: contact@ida-ebkes.eu
License: GPL
Description: Introduction
        ============
        
        This package is an add-on for Plone and part of the adi.simplesite-package-bundle.
        
        Add and place additional elements you need with ContentWellPortlets TTW, no viewlets-hassle.
        
        HidesPlone's default viewlets in top and footer area of the portal and adds some sample portlets there instead.
        
